The Ninja Coffee Bar is the best coffeehouse in town right on your counter top.

Learn more about the Ninja Coffee Bar™ at http://www.ninjacoffeebar.com. 

Get recipes for your Ninja Coffee Bar™ at http://www.ninjakitchen.com/recipes.
asset.author: Ninja Coffee Bar

transcripts: There is a lot of times that I just chose not to have coffee over ice because I knew it wouldn't turn out good. Now it's something I can look forward to in the afternoon. I've never had iced coffee this good as I do with the coffee ninja bar.
